[assistant] Fixed the failure and amended the existing commit.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Root cause:
[assistant] - `UUMailer` bytecode invokes `sun.misc.CharacterEncoder.encode(...)`, not `UUEncoder.encode(...)` directly.
[assistant] - The generated compatibility stub only provided `sun.misc.UUEncoder`, so loading `UUMailer` failed and `EmailTask` reported `Failed to initialise encoding: uu`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Fix:
[assistant] - Added generated `sun.misc.CharacterEncoder` stub.
[assistant] - Updated generated `sun.misc.UUEncoder` to extend `CharacterEncoder`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Updated commit:
[assistant] - `1e0935b80d Add EmailTask UU mail coverage test`
[assistant] 
[assistant] Working tree is clean. I did not run the Gradle test.
